swimming pool at Ross Snyder Recreation Center, far left and above. Right, park 
director Joyce Nishimuro leads a modern dance class at Aliso-Pico Recreation 
Center, and Latasha Miller, 6, swings at Queen Anne Recreation Center. ; Photo, 
COLOR, A brother and sister play at Ross Snyder. ; Photo, COLOR, Jefferson High 
