<HEADLINE>
<P>
ARSENIO HALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Patti LaBelle gave Arsenio Hall the best advice he'll probably ever hear. By 
Hall's being himself we are rewarded with a host who is sincere, interested in 
his guests, fun and, best of all, funny. Where I live we receive one channel. 
I'm grateful it happens to be the one that carries "The Arsenio Hall Show." 
</P>
<P>
JILL BROUILLARD 
</P>
<P>
Santa Barbara 
</P>
</TEXT>
