<HEADLINE>
<P>
POSITIVE ROLE MODEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding Nikki Finke's article on Willie Bogan, this story casts a refreshing 
glow on the idea of equality by focusing on Bogan's accomplishments and outlook 
rather than his race. Perhaps a few students ditching class during the Los 
Angeles teachers' strike will pick up the View section and learn from Bogan's 
example. He is an inspiration to young people of all ethnic backgrounds. 
