Wardair Canada, recently purchased by Canadian Airlines International, is 
offering service between Los Angeles and Toronto on Saturday and Sunday until 
June 18, with additional flights on Tuesday and Wednesday between June 20 and 
Sept. 12. The airline is flying between San Diego and Toronto on Saturday until 
Sept. 30. 
