<P>
JOINT VENTURES BUY 1,000 ACRES IN ACTON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Barry Alon of the Alon Organization has announced a 12-month single-family home 
development plan entailing $130 million in joint ventures for about 1,000 acres 
in Acton. 
