ACCIDENTS; AUTOMOBILE THEFTS; POLICE ASSAULTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; SHOOTINGS 
-- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; GANGS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
