<P>
GEPHARDT, RICHARD A; COELHO, TONY; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
DEMOCRATIC PARTY; FOLEY, THOMAS S; ANTHONY, BERYL JR 
</P>
