defense at third base has been a key to the Orioles' surge. Associated Press / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, Mickey Tettleton, a key player in Baltimore's tough 
defense, tags out Chicago's Matt Merullo. Associated Press; Photo, Cal Ripken's 
string of 29 games without an error ended Saturday. Associated Press 
</P>
